      "text": "優のもし恋を一番楽しみにしているのは優のファンだ\nその人達の気持ちになって考えてみよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Those who look forward to Yu’s Moshikoi the most are her fans.\nLet’s think from their perspective.",
        "id": ""
